        <h3>Lo Bénichou</h3>
        <img src="https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/5431395?s=400" class="responsive rounded margin-bottom">
        <a href="http://laurenbenichou.github.io/portfolio/"><span class="icon desktop"></span></span>Lo's Portfolio</a><br />
